Instead of `width="52" height="52"`, I think it will be easier to maintain with `:width="size" :height="size"`
and the following:
```javascript
export cont DEFAULT_SIZE = 52;

export default {
    props: {
        user: Object,
        size: {
            type: Number,
            default: DEFAULT_SIZE
        }
    }
}
```
